cards.name: Name

cards.helptext:
MAEASaM ID should be unique for all the resources in the database. The structure of the ID is as follows:

  • four characters to represent the resource mode
  • _
  • four characters to represent the person adding the resource
  • _
  • serial counter of six digits for the resources added by this person to this resource model

for example, the following ID is for the Actor resource model represented by ACTR, added by Mahmoud Abdelrazek represented by RZEK, and is the first actor resource for Mahmoud as represented by the counter 000001. Put together the ID should be 

ACTR_RZEK_000001

The choice of the characters representing your name is up to you. However please remember to check the list of all designations first as someone else might have chosen the same designation before. Also, once you have chosen your designation, it cannot be changed and should be used in all the IDs in all the resource models.
